00:55:15,828 --> 00:55:19,090
or do you write trying to make the samples

972
00:55:19,190 --> 00:55:20,251
transcend themselves,

973
00:55:20,331 --> 00:55:22,372
knowing that the mock-up may suffer as a result?

974
00:55:22,432 --> 00:55:24,874
And I'm a big fan of not limiting,

975
00:55:25,354 --> 00:55:27,515
the tools are there, truly as tools,

976
00:55:27,575 --> 00:55:29,457
let your imagination be as unbridled as possible.

977
00:55:29,537 --> 00:55:30,357
