00:57:35,115 --> 00:57:37,276
it's just too, I would rather be more present

1017
00:57:37,296 --> 00:57:40,599
with the musicians and just do this that way,

1018
00:57:40,759 --> 00:57:42,581
own this environment, own this situation

1019
00:57:42,641 --> 00:57:45,043
instead of trying to be half in one world

1020
00:57:45,083 --> 00:57:45,924
and half in another.

